320
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:33,120
Do you really not know
how your mother died?

321
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,280
Come back with me now.

322
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:35,600
I'll protect you.

323
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,680
